annotation.TEXT: Actually, yes, you do. I could have sworn you could sequence break here, but apparently not. If you don't read the V-JOLT report first, Jill won't even react to the chemicals in the room. You can grab the Empty Bottles and read the messages written on the walls, but that's about it. So if you're looking to speedrun, the V-JOLT route is pretty solidly a waste of time.
